.SH NAME
tomoyo_memory_ok \- Check memory quota.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" tomoyo_memory_ok
.BI "(void *ptr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ptr" 12
Pointer to allocated memory.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns true on success, false otherwise.

Returns true if \fIptr\fP is not NULL and quota not exceeded, false otherwise.

Caller holds tomoyo_policy_lock mutex.
